summary: The big news this week is AI may not be the economic savior that companies were hoping for. Sure, AI will help cut costs and make companies more profitable. At least, initially. What happens next is the big question. On Monday, the stock market dropped after an investment shop called Citrini Research released a hypothetical scenario about how the economy could look in 2028.
